deploy dev prisma server
 - go to prisma folder
 - prisma deploy -e ../config/dev.env (cmd)

deploy prod prisma server
 - prisma login (cmd)
 - go to prisma folder 
 - prisma deploy -e ../config/prod.env

 deploy prod heroku server
 - heroku create (first time) 
 - heroku config:set PRISMA_ENDPOINT=... (from prod convig)
 - heroku config:set PRISMA_SECRET=... (from prod convig)
 - heroku config:set JWT_SECRET=... (from prod convig)
 - git push heroku master (load latest code and run server)
